      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm having a massive issue with the API integration on the dev server. i'm getting a 504 gateway timeout every time i try to call the /auth/v2/token endpoint with a multi-part payload, but it works fine with simple JSON. i've checked the load balancer logs and it doesn't seem to be a timeout on the app side, more like the connection is just dropping mid-stream. can u look into why the multipart parsing is hanging the worker threads? i need this fixed for our deployment tonight.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
